thread.title_full: Peaches Boutique reviewed by DAWN TRAHAN

author: DAWN TRAHAN
title: DAWN TRAHAN
text: I was afraid to order because we lived s far away. But s glad we did it!! Very helpful. I called and gave style number of the dress, it took a minute to tell me it was in stock. I asked if it was the name brand MORILEE and not a knockoff off the dress. I was reassured that it was original. Fast friendly service. Dress came in quick and perfect!!
